<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.4.3">
<l>paṇṭiv vaiya maḷappāṉ ceṉṟumā valikaiyiṉir</l>
<l>koṇṭa vāḻit taṭakkaik kuṟaḷa ṉiṭameṉparāl</l>
<l>vaṇṭu pāṭum matuvār puṉalvan tiḻikāviri</l>
<l>aṇṭa nāṟum poḻilcūḻn taḻakār teṉṉaraṅkamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They truly say that the place of the dwarf with a broad discus[-bearing] hand</l>
<l>Who took the water in the hand of Māvali, coming long ago</l>
<l rend="indent">to measure this earth,</l>
<l>Is beautiful Araṅkam of the South, encircled by groves</l>
<l rend="indent">where the air is fragrant,</l>
<l>[And by] the Kāviri which flows, bringing waters where nectar floods</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] bees hum.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
